com.snapon.sbs.dns.email

Class EmailRequest

  • java.lang.Object
    • com.snapon.sbs.dns.email.EmailRequest

  • public class EmailRequest
extends Object
    This class is the representation of an email request made by any application. This class is then serialized by GSON and passed around where needed. If more class members are needed please remember to add the SerializedName annotation.

        public EmailRequest(String emailFrom,
            String subjectText,
            String bodyText,
            String systemName,
            String emailType,
            String createdBy,
            int templateId,
            String priority,
            boolean addUnSubLink,
            String unSubText)
        Overridden constructor
        Parameters:
        emailFrom - who is sending the email
        subjectText - what is the subject line of the email
        bodyText - what is in the body of the email
        systemName - the system the request came from
        emailType - what type of email is being sent
        createdBy - who created the email (username/email)
        templateId - the template ID the request is using
        priority - how urgent is the request
        addUnSubLink - if this request needs to add on the unsub link
        unSubText - the text to display the unsubscription details
